\left| \bigcup_{i=1}^{n} A_{i} \right| = \sum_{i=1}^{n} |A_{i}| - \sum_{1 \leq i < j \leq n} |A_{i} \cap A_{j}| \\ + \sum_{1 \leq i < j < k \leq n} |A_{i} \cap A_{j} \cap A_{k}| - \sum_{1 \leq i < j < k < l \leq n} |A_{i} \cap A_{j} \cap A_{k} \cap A_{l}| + \cdot \cdot \cdot
\displaystyle \bigcup A_n
\displaystyle \sum_n |A_n|
\displaystyle \sum_{i,j}|A_i\cap A_j|
\displaystyle \sum_{i,j,k}|A_i\cap A_j\cap A_k|
